%HES

G x y u z v =v Plus x y u /\ Plus u z v.
Plus x y u =μ (x=0 /\ y=u) \/ (x>0 /\ Plus (x-1) y (u-1)).
NotPlus x y u =v (x<>0 \/ y=u) /\ (x<=0 \/ NotPlus (x-1) y (u-1)).

